OL,5, A woman who struggled to access        
OL,6, night-time care for her dying father   
OL,7, has told the BBC he "shouldn't have    
OL,8, been expected to die in office hours". 
OL,10,FTracey Bennett said she was "completely
OL,11,Flost" when her dad Michael needed help.
OL,13,FMichael, who was in the final stages of
OL,14,Fcancer, had fallen late at night and   
OL,15,Fshe dialled the local NHS palliative   
OL,16,Fcare help-line but it was closed.      
OL,18,FAlmost 70% of the UK does not have a   
OL,19,Fconsistent 24-hour help-line for the   
OL,20,Fterminally ill, research suggests.     
